1.15
log
@Keep db_write_cmd() in the only place where it is used, just like we did
with db_show_regs().
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: db_write_cmd.c,v 1.14 2015/03/14 03:38:46 jsg Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: db_write_cmd.c,v 1.6 1996/02/05 01:57:25 christos Exp $	*/

/* 
